f whether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/49845/', '', 'Levocetirizine, Azelastine, Ketotifen, Trimethobenzamide', 'Ginkgo biloba, Aducanumab', 1767369485);
